data.description: Discover serene country living in this open-concept 3-bedroom, 2-bath home on just under an acre. The master suite, with its own ensuite bath, provides a private retreat. Enjoy the spacious kitchen, seamless living and dining areas, and relax on the large covered porch with panoramic views. The property includes a generous detached garage and workshop for versatile use. Embrace the tranquility and modern comforts of this countryside haven - your peaceful escape awaits!
